cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the PHY log level to an invalid value 'invalid' will cause configuration parsing failure as it's not one of the allowed log levels.
du.explanation_zh: 將 PHY 日誌級別設定為無效值 'invalid' 會導致配置解析失敗，因為它不是允許的日誌級別之一。
